create the form for category in my case i create a form where in category you can upload name,image of the category
then create model and migration for category where name,image, and slug will be created all are the strings


now create sub category and its child category view, model and migration

in sub categories we will create foreignkey(cat_id) name and slug laravel 8 has better method for foreign key constraint instead of old one

$table->foreignId('cat_id')->constrained('categories')->onUpdate('cascade') ->onDelete('cascade');
name and slug

in ->constrained() we will write parent table name ->constrained('categories ') model name 


in child categories we will create sub caterioes foriegn key ,name and slug 

$table->foreignId('sub_cat_id')->constrained('sub_categories')->onUpdate('cascade') ->onDelete('cascade');
name and slug






      
     
